<h2>Chapter 9: SaaS SEO by Company Stage</h2>
<p>There is no single SaaS SEO playbook. What works for a Series B company with 50 employees does not work for a pre-revenue startup with 2 founders.</p>
<h3>Pre-Revenue to $1M ARR</h3>
<p><strong>Priority:</strong> Validate demand and capture existing searches.</p>
<ul>
<li>Build comparison pages for every competitor in your space</li>
