<li>Optimize your G2 and Capterra profiles</li>
<li>Start a blog with 2 to 4 posts per month focused on BoFu and MoFu keywords</li>
</ul>
<p>At this stage, SEO is about capturing demand that already exists. Do not invest in ToFu awareness content yet. Every page should have a direct path to signup or demo.</p>
<h3>$1M to $10M ARR</h3>
